column1: All right, let's begin the operation!

Our first goal would be the Treasure
route, yes?

I'm sensing something Treasure-like
over... that way, towards 705.

That's where you were taken when
they captured you, right?

Yeah... Just thinkin' about it pisses
me off. That piece o' shit was so full
of herself.
So Alice is there now, huh?

You know, it does sort of look like a
castle.

A castle ruled by a Monarch—I admit,
it's rather fitting.
So we're headin' to the castle?

This Jail is crawling with Shadows,
though. Watch your backs out there.

Okay, I'll "watch your backs out
there."

Heheh, Sophie's inaugural heist as a
phantom thief! This'll be great!

We don't know the opposition we'll
face—be sure to switch out team
members when necessary.

Good point. We're at your beck and
call, Joker.
Wow... We really made it back to the Shibuya Jail.

It even went WOWOWOW and everything,
too...

Hmm, it seems Jails truly are different from
Palaces.
So, what do we do now?

Let's look around and see if we find a Desire
that didn't return to its owner.
But this place is rather large...

This is going to be like finding a needle in
a haystack. If only we could track it down
somehow...
Wait... I'm getting a faint scent!

There's a Treasure— I mean, a Desire over at
Shibuya Crossing!
Nice sniffin', Mona! Let's get over there!
